    {
      "id": "PopularPost241242",
      "post_content": "@Mode: Yo dawg, I heard you like horses so we put your horse on a horse so your horse can ride a horse.  \n  \nRegarding the effect itself, it's pretty powerful. Nowadays horsemanship is hardly ever used, so horsemanship is approximately equal to unblockable.  \n  \nAnother reason why it's good - permanent effect that is not an enchantment, so you can't get rid of it once it has been cast. You can destroy the creature, but that's a different story.",
      "posted_by": "Arachnos",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost241242\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">@Mode: Yo dawg, I heard you like horses so we put your horse on a horse so your horse can ride a horse.<br/><br/>Regarding the effect itself, it's pretty powerful. Nowadays horsemanship is hardly ever used, so horsemanship is approximately equal to unblockable.<br/><br/>Another reason why it's good - permanent effect that is not an enchantment, so you can't get rid of it once it has been cast. You can destroy the creature, but that's a different story.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '241242'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy54910\">Arachnos</span>\r\n                                (11/12/2013 6:29:20 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars